title: Neck Deep - Wishful Thinking
description:
Wishful Thinking is set to release next Tuesday Jan 14 but I figured since they streamed the entire album today that there was bound to be torrent sites with the album up and ready to download. WRONG. What is happening to the world of leakers and impatient music fans?! So I took it upon myself to do it. As always, support the artist(s) and buy the album if you liked it. Oh and please seed!
